{
  "stem": "22869.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Zolstadt is a little landmark on the map.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I remember when I was in Yad Vashem, I couldn't find it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They have a map of all concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was very upset-- I couldn't find the camp Zolstadt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The guy later explained to me that it was a real small camp, where they were making-- the Germans were producing the V2 and the V3s-- if you remember the rockets, against England that they were shooting out?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this, they had it all on the ground of that camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they brought us to Zolstadt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I stayed there three days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the whole Birkenau 1942 started repeating itself-- the beatings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, the dogs-- it-- it was almost like new to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All of a sudden, we're being mistreated again after-- after the little relief we had in the Kanada.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, we started crying, literally, all of our guys that we made such a stupid-- we would have been better to die in Auschwitz-- we didn't know that they were liberated-- than to go through all this hell again.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What for?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they took us from there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I stayed there are only three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was terrible-- beatings, I mean, day and night, day and night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took us from there to a second camp which was called Osterode.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Funny German words-- it was deep in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Again, underground V2 stuff, and they were strict.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like I said, it brought back all the picture, that the-- and all this sub-human treatment that we used to get in the 1942 when we first arrived to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For some reason-- I don't know what happened-- that for some reason we couldn't stay in this camp for too long of a period of time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it didn't happen to all of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
